		"description": "<p>Your weapon vibrates with thunderous energy, ready to shatter the composure and flesh of your foes.</p>\n<p>As part of the action to cast this spell, make an attack with your melee weapon. On a hit, in addition to normal weapon damage, the attack emits a thunderous boom, dealing an additional 1d8 thunder damage. If the target is concentrating, it has disadvantage on its next concentration check this turn.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, the target takes an additional 2d8 points of thunder damage on a hit. This increases to 3d8 at level 11 and 4d8 at level 17.</p>",
